uid":18477,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:57:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>哦～<br />\n你話Xitler the pooh<br />\n方丈好小器㗎</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a94f7e01ace5c416b42334ec02721f1ab7e2628","tid":2184821,"uid":8858,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:04.000Z","msg":"老施鬧習總係獨裁無上權力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45ea1040fb1da1e340b58deebe3aa982bb778af","tid":2184821,"uid":290118,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:33.000Z","msg":"留名等鞭屍<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 聖誕快樂"},{"pid":"8b6c9ebc41c263db23793771f988a3adc1b2004a","tid":2184821,"uid":317107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a45ea1040fb1da1e340b58deebe3aa982bb778af","tid":2184821,"uid":290118,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:58:33.000Z","msg":"留名等鞭屍<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 聖誕快樂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T00:59:39.000Z","msg":"人地係民選總統，係人民授權，咩叫唔尊重民意"},{"pid":"6f3e1599e7cb9d9e76dd0da0b4d7b3a75d576cf2","tid":2184821,"uid":262035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T01:00:16.000Z","msg":"咁你姐係話習大大有問題姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2755c28a5c556f516816c970ab2f67c87c1df7","tid":2184821,"uid":167394,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T01:00:35.000Z","msg":"唔好PO無用文章阻版位"},{"pid":"b0dcddbe856fcb414e32473f96cb6dc26a072591","tid":2184821,"uid":87573,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T01:02:37.000Z","msg":"永ching: 侵係加速師（美版）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf71